}

docs {
  # Get Category Content
  
  Public endpoint. Returns the content (description, price, image) for a single active subcategory.
  Returns **404** if the category does not exist, is inactive, or has no content yet.
  
  **URL param:** `{category}` — category ID
  
  **Response 200:**
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Профессиональная укладка плитки",
      "description": "Мастера выполняют укладку любых типов плитки...",
      "price": "от 50 TMT",
      "image_url": "http://localhost/storage/category-content/abc.webp"
    }
  }
  ```
  
  **Response 404** — category inactive or has no content:
  ```json
  { "message": "Not Found" }
  ```
}
